{"tid":1540874,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"粉嶺田家炳為校譽滅聲！","createTime":"2019-09-04T12:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T06:54:32.000Z","uid":307236,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"266d3164ae9adacc5c84170266ed46fde3bb9519","tid":1540874,"uid":307236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:48:05.000Z","msg":"幫post <br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n我係一個田家炳中學嘅普通學生<br />\n<br />\n話說我學校有個妹妹琴晚發夢去集會係巴士俾狗拉咗<br />\n雖然話請咗律師但仲未保釋到<br />\n好驚佢畀人拉咗去新屋嶺<br />\n學校又話處理緊但又撳住呢件事唔畀傳出嚟<br />\n依家啲高層為咗保住學校聲譽就抹殺學生知情權<br />\n定係想我哋成班學生變曬做港豬呀<br />\n越係唔想多人知我越要講出嚟<br />\n煲大佢等緊多人一齊參與罷課<br />\n同時溫馨提示各位手足發夢要小心<br />\n依家個社會荒謬到去和平集會都會畀狗捉<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n傻嘅都知林鄭諗住以退為進準備大搜捕<br />\n唔好同我講啲咩階段性勝利<br />\n因為今次輸就會輸一世<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手係tg廣傳同去連登推  我地做學生嘅真係好需要大家幫手!"},{"pid":"54bf45b21882337fb4644fb3146de315fdf50da8","tid":1540874,"uid":87988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:48:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ebabc13a728c4ef0f0baec2e5076f55aca4fbec","tid":1540874,"uid":8204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:48:46.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"ab1e67ba3999bdbbb161efd5d4234e8037e15e5e","tid":1540874,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:48:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e03b4ef66a75e497664ae5159a56bff66d75ff4","tid":1540874,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:49:07.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"e7f7cb27e0862a2ec61f616469a0923c86137df9","tid":1540874,"uid":71997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"266d3164ae9adacc5c84170266ed46fde3bb9519","tid":1540874,"uid":307236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:48:05.000Z","msg":"幫post <br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n我係一個田家炳中學嘅普通學生<br />\n<br />\n話說我學校有個妹妹琴晚發夢去集會係巴士俾狗拉咗<br />\n雖然話請咗律師但仲未保釋到<br />\n好驚佢畀人拉咗去新屋嶺<br />\n學校又話處理緊但又撳住呢件事唔畀傳出嚟<br />\n依家啲高層為咗保住學校聲譽就抹殺學生知情權<br />\n定係想我哋成班學生變曬做港豬呀<br />\n越係唔想多人知我越要講出嚟<br />\n煲大佢等緊多人一齊參與罷課<br />\n同時溫馨提示各位手足發夢要小心<br />\n依家個社會荒謬到去和平集會都會畀狗捉<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n傻嘅都知林鄭諗住以退為進準備大搜捕<br />\n唔好同我講啲咩階段性勝利<br />\n因為今次輸就會輸一世<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手係tg廣傳同去連登推  我地做學生嘅真係好需要大家幫手!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:49:53.000Z","msg":"轉去皇仁，自由空氣"},{"pid":"64ebc35d8a00fbb0c806c36c81c4af256c7f9730","tid":1540874,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:50:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fca04c64ed1ff3e09b2230ad841f5552facc1a0d","tid":1540874,"uid":151933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d680597c968e31025c063972a2cc0dc987326fb6","tid":1540874,"uid":155412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:51:36.000Z","msg":"藍絲校長叫小學生出街帶糖  多謝pop